WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.000
Welcome to the mini story for Day of the Dead.

2
00:00:04.500 --> 00:00:07.500
Did AJ arrive in Guatemala on Christmas?

3
00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:12.000
No, AJ arrived in Guatemala on the Day of the Dead.

4
00:00:12.500 --> 00:00:15.500
Where did AJ arrive?

5
00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:20.000
In Guatemala. AJ arrived in Guatemala.

6
00:00:20.500 --> 00:00:24.000
When did AJ arrive in Guatemala?

7
00:00:24.500 --> 00:00:29.000
AJ arrived in Guatemala on the Day of the Dead, November 1st.

8
00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:34.000
Was AJ curious about the holiday?

9
00:00:34.500 --> 00:00:40.000
Yes, he was curious. AJ was curious about the holiday.

10
00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:46.000
What was he curious about? The holiday! He was curious about the holiday.

11
00:00:47.000 --> 00:00:52.000
So he went to the cemetery to see what was happening.

12
00:00:53.000 --> 00:00:58.000
Where did he go? To the cemetery. He went to the cemetery.

13
00:00:59.000 --> 00:01:04.000
Did he go to the cemetery or did he go to the airport?

14
00:01:05.000 --> 00:01:10.000
He went to the cemetery. He didn't go to the airport.

15
00:01:11.000 --> 00:01:15.000
Why did he go to the cemetery?

16
00:01:16.000 --> 00:01:21.000
To see what was happening. He wanted to see what was happening.

17
00:01:22.000 --> 00:01:27.000
What he found was quite interesting.

18
00:01:28.000 --> 00:01:33.000
Was it boring? No! It wasn't boring, it was interesting.

19
00:01:34.000 --> 00:01:38.000
The atmosphere was like a party.

20
00:01:39.000 --> 00:01:44.000
Was the atmosphere like a funeral? 

21
00:01:45.000 --> 00:01:50.000
No, no. The atmosphere was not like a funeral. It was like a party!

22
00:01:51.000 --> 00:01:56.000
There were people everywhere. Families were sitting around the graves...

23
00:01:57.000 --> 00:02:02.000
...of their dead ancestors. They cleaned the graves and added flowers.

24
00:02:03.000 --> 00:02:08.000
AJ admired the colorful flowers and decorations.

25
00:02:09.000 --> 00:02:15.000
In the United States, cemeteries are always somber and quiet.

26
00:02:16.000 --> 00:02:22.000
But here in Guatemala, the cemetery is like a festival!
